My #HoneyDew this week is Greg Fitzsimmons! Greg shares a story about being rejected by the first girl he asked out and how that impacted his dating life. Greg also talks about how and why he finally stopped drinking, getting fired from a job, and mourning the death of his father. We cover a lot on this episode! Check it out!
